data.description: This beautifully charming 2-story home is backed to a green belt and located in an established neighborhood! Enjoy entertaining guests with the convenient open floor plan and watch a movie in the media/ theater wired room upstairs.  With living areas upstairs and downstairs, you will have plenty of space to host your guests and house your family. The kitchen has a beautiful island and breakfast nook with granite counter tops and built in appliances. Enjoy having two dining areas for eating or relax in front of your cozy fireplace and have a snack. If you love connecting with nature, feel the breeze while sitting on your front porch in the shade or go lounging in the backyard.  Only 10 minutes outside of the city of Austin, and 30 minutes from downtown and the Domain! This home is in a great location, 5 minutes from Walmart, 7 minutes from HEB, 20 minutes from Typhoon Texas Water Park and the Stonehill Center, and only 30 minutes from: Kalahari Resorts, Dell Diamond, and Rock'N River Water Park.
